      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON BIDEN (1) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the minors latest when third (20.08) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Top chance in this line up. WAIKARIE KOBY (8) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (19.89) at this track in a Other. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can find the frame this time. BLUE ENERGY (7) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at this track over 342m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in this for a long way. OUR BELLA ROSE (4) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
